{"tid":1801103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽聞中聯辦係南昌站上蓋匯璽有700個單位 下面個商場V Walk仲幾靚","createTime":"2019-12-28T11:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T06:37:04.000Z","uid":302,"like":79,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"ce3f6fad4cf4d210c6cdf8ef56cf02243a01a445","tid":1801103,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"係時候要去行街街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nV Walk是一個由新鴻基地產發展的商場，位於九龍深水埗區深水埗匯璽的基座，是南昌站的上蓋發展項目，於2019年7月26日開業。[1]商場以We Walk Together為主題，（V代表Vivid），強調商場以年輕人消費和活力為主。雖然商場規模比較少，但集團仍以區內大型旗艦商場作為招徠，同時希望成為西九龍區內地標。[2]商場原本命名為「V&middot;Walk」，於開幕前半年再更名為「V Walk」。"},{"pid":"973f707164cb9a67394deac64e2931911f7cf661","tid":1801103,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:29:39.000Z","msg":"商場店舖每呎租金約100至200元，面積約700至1,500平方呎，分為6大主題區域，包括潮流服裝、美容及化妝品、鐘錶珠寶、電子影音、特色餐飲及大型超市。其中商場內租用面積最多的商戶為佔地1.5萬方呎的fusion by ParknShop超級市場，內設熟食櫃位。另外，已公佈進駐商場的大型租戶還包括朗思國際幼稚園。[6]而佔地近8000呎的嘉禾V Walk戲院則是第二大租戶，設5個影院，400個座位。<br />\n<br />\n租戶還包括7間鐘錶珠寶店（周生生、周大福、六福珠寶、英皇鐘錶珠寶、謝瑞麟、AGATHA Paris和PANDORA）、化妝品店benefit和Guerlain、以至UNIQLO。而服裝店主要包括bread n butter、Levi's、initial、眼鏡88、SKECHERS、AIGLE、sports b.、bauhaus和Timberland等。其他租戶以蔘茸藥材店、健康產品及藥房為主。<br />\n<br />\n餐飲商戶包括太興集團旗下的TEA WOOD茶木和敏華冰廳、牛角、滋味廚房、一芳水果茶、台灣擔仔麵度小月、日本居酒屋漁釧、Italian Tomato、滿記甜品、Starbucks、曲奇四重奏、越式餐廳囍越WHAT THE PHO、牛涮鍋もっと、華御結、TOM N TOMS COFFEE、Bugis@叻沙‧海南雞飯、中國飲品店恋暖の初茶、大家樂、H&auml;agen-Dazs、和平飯店、紅螞蟻餐廳、小富臨、健康料理原味家作、聰嫂私房甜品、校長廚房、Get Fresh O2O 日本厳選フルーツ専門店、天仁茗茶、美心西餅、A-1麵包和峰壽司等。[7]部分食肆設座位等候區供食客等候。"},{"pid":"d85484a2588831b5e690d750db07dce578e829a2","tid":1801103,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:30:42.000Z","msg":"新地(016)南昌站匯璽III在近日社會動盪下低價開盤，掀起入票認購潮。項目今日截止認購登記，受啟德新盤高開刺激，今天單日勁收逾千票，地產代理瘋傳，有一組公司客大手入近300票(A及B組各入148票)，以每票20萬元計算，動用入票資金已高達近6,000萬元，擬大手掃入70個單位。市傳該大手客為中聯辦。本報向中聯辦查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n就市傳中聯辦大手入票，新地副董事總經理雷霆回覆本報稱，「基於客人私隱，不作回應」。"},{"pid":"0ca1d563d12517663890df96eaca78a57aa3fabc","tid":1801103,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:31:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71b1e838402e224b6bd2b47c7fe7d9a0e4887644","tid":1801103,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190919/60060307?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60060307%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNSL1bdbhbSvxCnYHZ8iA0HE%3D&h=eeebc0ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F60060307%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=47533acb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190919/60060307?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a>"},{"pid":"5e4a21a25ea78de0c0b446983add25a234864be7","tid":1801103,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:32:23.000Z","msg":"700 x 1000 萬係幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3371ecf34ea00357881e0a712218fba76111b7","tid":1801103,"uid":11895,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:33:14.000Z","msg":"70啊700"},{"pid":"43bfe12a5fc9405ef6f484f4bfec1660159108bc","tid":1801103,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:33:56.000Z","msg":"<a hr